                    <div class="h3" style="color: var(--color-red-600)">{{ systemIcon('error') }}&nbsp; When not to use</div>
                    <ul class="bulleted-list">
                        <li>If the user has 4 or fewer options to choose from, and can only choose one, use <strong>radio buttons</strong></li>
                        <li>If the user has 4 or fewer options to choose from, and can choose more than one, use <strong>checkboxes</strong></li>
                        <li>If the user can select only one option, and there are more than 4 to choose from, use a <strong>select box</strong></li>
